-year-old Olympic record[in the 100-meter hurdles].\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"your 24-year-old Olympic record[in\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter hurdles\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m like,I didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know I had it,so OK!\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same thing with bringing back the gold.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same thing\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this year, more than any other, we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve sent a great team to Paris.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999998121851094, \"rank\": 1.878152234563218e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"a great team\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If this isthe year, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to be a joyous time.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"a joyous time\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:The U.S. team is one of the hardest teams to make.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. team\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest teams\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 