", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s their first Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That makes you hungry.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the three that made the team [Richardson, Melissa Jefferson and Twanisha Terry] are from the same camp.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.625788952686177e-14, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melissa Jefferson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Twanisha Terry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the same camp\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have the same coach [Dennis Mitchell].\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Mitchell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.943358800427441e-35, \"text\": \"Dennis Mitchell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627