0080\\u0099s what progress is.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what progress\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You want each generation to get better and better.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each generation\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, we have the Diamond League.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999959950401, \"rank\": 3.0226392705745895e-09, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, we didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have meets in the states.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the states\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So you had to go to Europe.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re all riding the bus together, riding on planes together, riding on the trains.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the bus\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"planes\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the trains\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:That was when I should have been on top of the world.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I was, for a moment, because I had broken the American record for the 100-meter hurdles, in college.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.997622600811796, \"rank\": 0.0023667697316393822, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter hurdles\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statisticians are saying,If she just runs what she ran a couple months,we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re gonna have a medal.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statisticians\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I got to the Games and the bottom fell out.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran slower than I ever ran.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a problem.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took three years before I was ever diagnosed.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was constantly losing weight, tired all the time, couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t sleep.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\