dles, everything was blurry.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hurdles\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could never see the hurdles clearly.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hurdles\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had learned to negotiate going over those hurdles.\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those hurdles\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What the rhythm is.\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rhythm\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s eight steps from the blocks to the first hurdle.\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s eight steps\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"the blocks\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"the first hurdle\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s three steps in between.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s three steps\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Five steps off the last hurdle to the finish line.\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last hurdle\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to run in rhythm.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythm\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because if I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m runn